measurements.description: Five flowers on three simultaneous inflorescences at one node, four flowers on three simultaneous infloresceences at a second node, one flower on one infloresence; sepals and petals dark violet-purple, white proximally, white tips; broad lip darker violet purple, white proximally, dark purple veins in throat; column and anther cap white; substance average; texture shiny.
